the damn beer can.

26:43.394 --> 26:44.520
Mmm!

26:49.608 --> 26:51.694
Rayleen Mosely?

26:51.777 --> 26:53.070
Hi, Krystal.

26:53.154 --> 26:54.572
Hey.

26:54.655 --> 26:56.824
It's been a minute.

26:56.907 --> 26:59.660
Mm-hmm.

26:59.744 --> 27:02.288
Since, uh...

27:02.371 --> 27:05.124
Pavo Possum Fest.

