28:05.726 --> 28:07.311
Isn't that sweet?

28:07.395 --> 28:08.938
Perfectly appropriate.

28:09.021 --> 28:10.314
Yes, precious.

28:10.398 --> 28:12.733
Zero's the number of infinity.

28:13.776 --> 28:15.277
Is that right?

28:15.361 --> 28:17.571
- Yeah.
- Well...

28:17.655 --> 28:21.409
Troop Zero, welcome to Birdie Scouting.

28:23.160 --> 28:26.163
